COMMAND where-used
SYNOPSIS: python3 scripts/cypilot.py where-used --id <id> [options]
DESCRIPTION: Find all references to an Cypilot ID using template-based parsing. Scans all registered Cypilot artifacts.

ARGUMENTS:
  id  <string>  required  Cypilot ID to find references for

OPTIONS:
  --artifact  <path>  Limit search to specific artifact (optional)
  --include-definitions  <boolean>  Include definitions in results (default: references only)

EXIT CODES:
